column1: Interestingly, apoptosis induced by NF - kappa B suppression, in contrast to that induced by TPEN ( N, N, N ', N ' - tetrakis [ 2 - pyridylmethyl] ethylenediamine) or soluble Fas ligand ( CD95), was observed in the absence of active death effector proteases caspase - 1 - like ( IL - 1 converting enzyme), caspase - 3 - like ( CPP32 / Yama / apopain), and caspase - 6 - like and without cleavage of caspase - 3 substrates poly ( ADP - ribose) polymerase and DNA fragmentation factor - 45.
